{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 641297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 132703, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "倩，见信如晤。思来想去，我们互道一声再见吧。\n遇到你是我的幸运，我曾经很快乐。然而世殊时异，可惜我们不能走到一起白头，其中原因部分归于你我的品性，也归于命运的作弄。祝你快乐，找到自己的幸福。", "timestamp": 1606805673, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 641303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 132703, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 分手带师", "timestamp": 1606805759, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 641325, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 132703, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 林觉民《与妻书》，可以参考一下先烈的诀别信", "timestamp": 1606806101, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 641350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 132703, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "羡慕还能收到分手信的人。想当初自己分手，说完最后一句话，他起身就走，从此一别两宽，再无瓜葛，结果自己花了两年的时间来消化这件事。建议洞主不论怎么写，写清楚分手的原因吧，别让对方因分的不清不楚而痛苦。", "timestamp": 1606806483, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 641351, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 132703, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "花店不开了，花继续开", "timestamp": 1606806502, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 132703, "reply": 5, "tag": null, "text": "分手信应该怎么写", "timestamp": 1606805067, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606818530, "url": "", "vote": {}}}